OL,3,CSwimming club at risk of closing
OL,5,FA Borders sports club says it is at
OL,6,Frisk of closing if it cannot secure
OL,7,Fnew members to help cover costs.
OL,9,FCoaches at Duns Amateur Swimming Club
OL,10,Fsay the club needs around 20 extra
OL,11,Fpeople just to break even.
OL,13,FThe club has a rich history of
OL,14,Ftraining Olympic-standard athletes,
OL,15,Fbut its membership has fallen, and
OL,16,Fmore young people are needed to sign
OL,17,Fup before the club is forced to close
OL,18,Fits doors.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/6
