OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1775751065
OL,3,CSwimming club at risk of closing
OL,5,FEllie Spence, the chair of Duns
OL,6,FAmateur Swimming Club, said: "Sadly,
OL,7,Fover the last few years, our
OL,8,Fmembership numbers have dipped to the
OL,9,Fpoint where costs aren't being covered
OL,10,Fon a monthly basis, and we're real
OL,11,Frisk of having to close.
OL,13,F"We don't want that to happen. We want
OL,14,Fto be able to keep offering swimming
OL,15,Fcoaching to young people in the boat
OL,16,Fin Duns in the surrounding area.
OL,18,F"But we need our members membership to
OL,19,Fincrease, we need more swimmers in the
OL,20,Fpool."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
