PN,35903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1775751065
OL,3,CSwimming club at risk of closing
OL,5,FThe club's swimming team is run by
OL,6,Fvolunteers made up of locals and
OL,7,Fparents who have a passion for
OL,8,Fcoaching and swimming.
OL,10,FHead Coach Morag Stephens said: "It is
OL,11,Fa great shame because swimming is
OL,12,Ffabulous.
OL,14,F"One (of my children) has left the
OL,15,Fswimming club and I have two others
OL,16,Fstill in the swimming club, and they
OL,17,Fall get a great amount of joy,
OL,18,Ffitness, friendship out of it.
OL,26,@vD@FpmvD@Upn
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1775751065
OL,3,CSwimming club at risk of closing
OL,5,F"And knowing that that could extend to
OL,6,Fso many more kids, it's really
OL,7,Fdisappointing that we haven't got
OL,8,Fenough swimmers at the moment."
OL,10,FThe pool is unusual in the Borders
OL,11,Fbecause it is run by the community,
OL,12,Frather than local organisation Live
OL,13,FBorders on behalf of the council.
OL,15,FThe volunteers successfully run more
OL,16,Fthan 500 lessons a week.
OL,18,FThe club says teaching swimming as a
OL,19,Fsport, not just an activity, gives
OL,20,Fyoung people a chance to travel to
OL,21,Fcompetitions at the weekends.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
