PN,35905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1775751065
OL,3,CSwimming club at risk of closing
OL,5,FAmelie Spence said: "I joined when I
OL,6,Fwas in Primary Five.
OL,8,F"I remember the first time I came
OL,9,Fhere. I stayed in the changing rooms
OL,10,Fand I hid because I was so scared of
OL,11,Ftrying this new thing with all these
OL,12,Fbig, scary people.
OL,14,F"But eventually I made it, and it was
OL,15,Fit was great. I loved it, and that
OL,16,Factually helped me with other things,
OL,17,Ftrying new, different things."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/6
