OL,3,CSwimming club at risk of closing
OL,5,FWith the Commonwealth Games returning
OL,6,Fto Scotland this summer, the club
OL,7,Fhopes it could inspire the next
OL,8,Fgeneration of Olympic athletes.
OL,10,FAs such, its volunteers are determined
OL,11,Fto keep the swimming club open, and
OL,12,Fwelcome new members with open arms.
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
